I) Use without Installing
-------------------------

    $ python2.7 xml_to_json.py -r xregion -f xflow -p source_dir -o output.json


II) Use after Installing
------------------------

    To Install:
    	$ sudo python2.7 setup.py install -f


    a) Use as a command from the Shell:
        $ xml_to_json -r xregion -f xflow -p 2 -o output.json


    b) Use as an imported module from a Python program:
	    >>> from xml_to_json import XMLToJson
	    >>> XMLToJson('xxregion', 'xxflow', 'projects/imex/2', 'outputt.json').run()
